|----------|------|------|
| CoreDefense: Mindustry X | `core-defense` | `core-defense-preview.html` |
| CyberFortune 012 | `cyber-fortune` | `cyber-fortune-preview.html` |
| Pulse Protocol: Neon Beat | `pulse-protocol` | `pulse-protocol-preview.html` |
